0.02 - 10/09/2020
=================

BUGFIXES
 - Polarisation now rotates into component frame
 - Moderators now initialize random polarisation
FEATURES
 - Added several kernels:
    - Isotropic kernel with support for different polarisation interactions (WIP)
    - Polariser and analyser kernels
    - Beamstop kernel
    - Sphere interior kernel
 - Added optional support for double precision in kernels on supported platforms
 - Added neutron buffer component macros
 - Added errors to detector outputs
 - Added wavelength variable to detectors
 - Added C-style comments and disable flag to instrument definition files
 - Added neutron path tracing functionality to instrument visualisations
HOUSEKEEPING
 - Pythonized kernel import scripts